<feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>Anlatabildiklerim - araçlar</title><link href="https://gunluk.orkungunay.com/" rel="alternate"></link><link href="https://gunluk.orkungunay.com/feeds/araclar.atom.xml" rel="self"></link><id>https://gunluk.orkungunay.com/</id><updated>2018-03-17T00:42:00+03:00</updated><entry><title>Pomodoro nun Pratik Kullanımı</title><link href="https://gunluk.orkungunay.com/pomodoro-crontab.html" rel="alternate"></link><published>2018-03-14T17:14:00+03:00</published><updated>2018-03-17T00:42:00+03:00</updated><author><name>orkung</name></author><id>tag:gunluk.orkungunay.com,2018-03-14:/pomodoro-crontab.html</id><summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Pomodoro en kolay nasıl hayata dahil edilir&lt;/p&gt;</summary><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Pomodoro disipliniyle çalışmak için ( 25 dk. çalış, 5 dk. mola ver ),
terminal'den çalışan bir app aradım, python/zsh/nodejs app'larını denedim,
hiçbirisi istediğim verimlilikte değildi, sonunda kendim hazırladım, son derece
de basit oldu, crontab'ı şöyle düzenledim;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;*/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;30&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;      &lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nv"&gt;usr&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nv"&gt;bin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nv"&gt;notify&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;send&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;Work&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="mi"&gt;25&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;      &lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nv"&gt;usr&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nv"&gt;bin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nv"&gt;notify&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;send&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;Break&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="mi"&gt;55&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;      &lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nv"&gt;usr&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nv"&gt;bin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nv"&gt;notify&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;send&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;Break&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Her yarım saatte bir &lt;code&gt;Work&lt;/code&gt;, saati her 25 ve 55 geçtiğinde ise &lt;code&gt;Break&lt;/code&gt; gönderiyor.
böylece pomodoro döngüsü sağlanıyor.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kısacası, eğer hızlıca yapılabilir geliyorsa, önce yapılmısına bakmak yerine,
kendin yaptığında daha verimli oluyormuş.&lt;/p&gt;</content><category term="pomodoro"></category></entry></feed>